{
  "_comment": "Version: 1 | Path: infra/c12_workflow/workflows/extract_and_ingest.json | Description: D-020 R-100-081 v2 ingestion workflow — webhook upload → MinIO put (raw bytes) → C13 POST /analyze → poll /status until terminal → read MinIO artifacts (chunks.jsonl + run_manifest.json + embeddings) → POST C7 /ingest-chunks → respond. Supersedes ingest_text_source.json and chunk_and_track.json (both marked active:false in this session, deleted in session 7). Import via `docker compose exec c12 n8n import:workflow --input=/workflows/extract_and_ingest.json` after bringing the stack up. @relation implements:R-100-080 R-100-081 R-100-125 R-400-220 R-400-223",
